## 8. Regulatory Compliance Framework

### Regulatory Standards Compliance
All production deployments MUST comply with institutional regulatory requirements:

- **SEC**: Securities and Exchange Commission (5% max position concentration, 2% max VaR)
- **FINRA**: Financial Industry Regulatory Authority (best execution, real-time trade reporting)  
- **MiFID II**: Markets in Financial Instruments Directive (0.5% position reporting threshold)
- **CFTC**: Commodity Futures Trading Commission (position limits, swap reporting)
- **ESMA**: European Securities and Markets Authority (transparency requirements)

